Valencia on Saturday defeated Spanish giants FC Barcelona to win the Copa Del Rey. The defending champions lost 2-1 in a match that may be the last for the under-fire Coach Ernesto Valverde. The defeat denied Barcelona a fifth consecutive Copa Del Rey victory. When superstar Lionel Messi pulled one goal back in the second half, many expected a comeback. But the Valencia players held on for a memorable victory, even missing two open chances to kill off the game. Details shortlyâ€¦